room_title: Escape room "Mad Hatter" by Escape Countdown in Sarasota
room_description: While on a hike through the woods, you stumbled and found yourself tumbling through a long, dark tunnel. When you stopped, you found yourself in a strange new place. It appears you have interrupted a tea party. In order to find your way back home, you need to find clues and solve riddles that will open the door to home.
